metadata.description: As with all high-quality `anarchic` NFT shows, Assholios is based on a super limited collection of 500 extremely unique and mind-blowing characters that rule the Ethereum blockchain in terms of catalogue, assisted by the very highest standards of artwork and traits specifically targeted to fit each of the alien protagonists, in order to assist each individual personality. The Assholios you buy automatically become your gateway to a VIP members-only area. Where top-secret inventions and gadgetry can be unlocked and revealed. Visit www.assholios.com/mint for more details.
